Revision history for Perl extension Tk::XMLViewer.

0.18_92
	- fixed closing tag indentation (bug introduced in 0.18_91)
	- fixed "make demo"

0.18_91
	- massive speed improvement from large files by defering
	  tagAdd calls

0.18
	- -showxpath option for tkxmlview
	- BalloonInfo showing XPath information
	- new menu item: XPath to Selection
	- tkxmlview has now a standard menu
	- file history in tkxmlview (for now the history is lost when
	  quitting the application)

0.17
	- -loaddtd option for tkxmlview
	- Pod for tkxmlview
	- -xmlparserargs option for insertXML
	- fix for Tk804.026

0.16
	- tkxmlview uses Tk::HistEntry if available
	- Win32 compat fix for tkxmlview
	- can handle unicode with Tk804
	- fix for -elide/-state confusion

0.15
	- revert usage of ProtocolEncoding => 'UTF-8'
	- Open URL feature in tkxmlview

0.14
	- using ProtocolEncoding => 'UTF-8'
	- new options -tagcolor, -attrkeycolor, -attrvalcolor, -commentcolor
	- documented use of tagConfigure

0.13
	- unicode compatibility with perl 5.7.0 and perl 5.6.1
	  NOTE: older versions of Tk::XMLViewer will not work with perl 5.6.1
                or newer!

0.12
	- pod additions
	- bug fixes
	- GetInfo method

0.11
	- fixed call order of MainWindow and GetOptions in tkxmlview

0.10
	- Unicode handling on older perls with Unicode::String enabled
	- new Info dialog with DTD and other information
	- comments are also shown

0.09
	- limited Unicode handling
	- fixed numerous bugs
	- new methods: DumpXML, ShowToDepth, XMLMenu, OpenDepth

0.01  Tue Jan 18 13:19:26 2000
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.19

